    weatherSealSpec: `San Antonio weather-seal specifications: EPDM rubber bottom seal withstands Hill Country UV and thermal cycling across the widest temperature swing of any major Texas city (5F to 108F annual range). Top and side astragal seals require UV-stabilized silicone or EPDM compound. Post-Uri 2021 freeze-crack damage on vinyl seals drove mass replacement to cold-rated EPDM across Bexar County. Limestone-alkaline dust from Hill Country soils abrades standard vinyl faster than neutral-pH-environment installs. Seal replacement typically runs $120-$260 per door.`,
