    smartHomeIntegration: `San Antonio smart-home integration: LiftMaster MyQ and Genie Aladdin Connect dominate $400K+ San Antonio homes. CPS Energy's municipally owned grid provides stronger reliability than ERCOT-only providers, reducing battery-backup urgency compared to Houston or Dallas markets. MyQ integration with Ring and Amazon Key is standard in Stone Oak and Alamo Heights. LiftMaster 87504 Secure View with integrated camera is popular in suburban Far North Side and Helotes for package-theft prevention. Licensed installer setup runs $75-$150.`,
